Example:

1024 â†’ 10000000000 â†’ 1 bit

512 â†’ 1000000000 â†’ 1 bit

1 â†’ 1 â†’ 1 bit

Since all have same bit count,
just sort normally ascending.

Final:

[1,2,4,8,16,32,64,128,256,512,1024]
